item.title: Ayushmann Khurrana’s ‘Doctor G’ set for OTT debut on Netflix
item.description: Ayushmann Khurrana’s ‘Doctor G’ set for OTT debut on Netflix Mumbai: Hindi film star Ayushmann Khurrana’s Doctor G will be released for streaming on Netflix December 11.
